paragraphs.title: Using drill to query flat json
Overall json structure
paragraphs.text: select * from dfs.my.`NYET.jsonl` t where  event = 'message' LIMIT 10

paragraphs.title: Number of messages per user
paragraphs.text:
select t.`from`.first_name, count(*) 
from dfs.my.`NYET.jsonl` t 
where  
event = 'message' 
and ( lower(t.`from`.username) not like '%bot' or t.`from`.username is null)
group by t.`from`.first_name 
order by 2 desc

paragraphs.title: First message date
paragraphs.text: select min(t.`date`) from dfs.my.`NYET.jsonl` t where  event = 'message'  LIMIT 30

paragraphs.title: Bot's messages
paragraphs.text: select * from dfs.my.`NYET.jsonl` t where  event = 'message' and t.`from`.first_name = 'Nyetbot' LIMIT 10

paragraphs.title: Messages per user in last 6 month
paragraphs.text:
select t.`from`.first_name, count(*) 
from dfs.my.`NYET.jsonl` t 
where  
event = 'message' 
and ( lower(t.`from`.username) not like '%bot' or t.`from`.username is null)
and t.`date` >= 1491523200
group by t.`from`.first_name 
order by 2 desc

paragraphs.title: Symbols per user in last 6 month
paragraphs.text:
select t.`from`.first_name, sum(length(t.`text`)) 
from dfs.my.`NYET.jsonl` t 
where  
event = 'message' 
and ( lower(t.`from`.username) not like '%bot' or t.`from`.username is null)
and t.`date` >= 1491523200
group by t.`from`.first_name 
order by 2 desc
